race.comment: PAW XENA (7) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 4 last run (25.25) at this track. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from seven starts. Likely to be in the finish again. TARAWI THERESE (1) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 4.5 lengths at Geelong in a handy 22.26 beating Prison Break. Has the coveted inside box and has a good record over this journey. Can make it two on the bounce. PAW TORONTO (3) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (25.54) last time out at this track. Has a strong winning record at this journey. Expected to be in this for a long way. CANYA ULTIMATE (2) was below best last time at Geelong (26.00) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 1.5 lengths fourth. Already a winner from this draw.
